## Results
- Strong positive Pearson correlation (r = 0.7828)
- Negative Headlines: 39%
- Neutral Headlines: 34%
- Positive Headlines: 27%
Although the correlation was strong, the p-value (0.0657) indicated that the relationship was not statistically significant at the 5% significance level due to the small sample size.
